name: I Love University of Dayton T-Shirt
description:
How can you show your love for University of Dayton without a shirt that says "I love UD"?! This shirt is currently being sold on campus but, for a limited time, we are offering the same shirt to University of Dayton alumni. Featuring the classic I ‚ù§ NY design on the front, everyone will know where your collegiate allegiance lies. 

The back includes some of the most unique things about University of Dayton, such as Crazy Hazing Lady, 9-Holes, the Pub and many more. Check out the image and help support this student designed shirt. Only 300 were produced and our cups are empty, so we need your order! SMALLS HAVE SOLD OUT (Shipping Note: We use the standard Priority Mail shipping rate of $5.00 and each additional shirt is another $1.00)
